{"title":"湘江水九十九道弯","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江水九十九道弯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江水九十九道弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的道路多艰难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十年前风雨夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声惊雷起狂澜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山头烈火烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤起工农千百万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征踏破千里雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席同咱共苦甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全中国的人民感谢他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他和人民心相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心连心革命干到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心连心红旗永向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江水九十九道弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的形势大发展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十年后天地变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里春风乌云散。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门上红灯亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得四海红艳艳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利要跨万重关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席走在最前边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普天下的人民跟着他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他和人民心相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心连心革命干到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心连心红旗永向前！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}